    "body": "## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Launch FF and rotate the device from portrait to landscape mode.\r\n2. Observe the minimized tip while the keyboard is invoked.\r\n3. Dismiss the keyboard and observe the carousel tips.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\nThe carousel tips should be completely visible when the keyboard is invoked/dismissed in landscape mode.\r\n\r\n### Actual behavior\r\nCarousel tips are improperly displayed as cutoff in landscape mode when the keyboard is invoked/dismissed.\r\n\r\nThe issue occurs whenever the user returns to homescreen and the keyboard is invoked automatically.\r\n\r\n### Device information\r\n\r\n* Android device: Huawei P9 Lite (Android 8); Huawei P20 (Android 10).\r\n* Focus version:  93.0.2 (Build 352522329 93.0a1-20210906031657).\r\n\r\nPlease note that the issue could not be reproduced on other devices.\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/89388888/132832235-7b3184e1-e41d-4c41-8850-438a994ba189.mp4\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/89388888/132832243-cae3f5a6-a448-4629-9c93-4fe5975f306c.mp4\r\n\r\n",
